{"tid":628684,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"度蜜月應該邊個比？","createTime":"2018-04-14T05:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T06:33:20.000Z","uid":172607,"like":8,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"58668367e648959e6ecdd56bb74d8786af136f5e","tid":628684,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:44:58.000Z","msg":"借朋友account 用<br />\n<br />\n一向同男朋友去旅行都係佢六我四咁<br />\n當地洗費全部自己俾<br />\n識佢咁耐都知佢份人比較計較金錢 好鍾意錢<br />\n但我覺得既然愛佢就要包容同接受佢性格<br />\n籌備緊結婚野 講開度蜜月<br />\n佢竟然話都係普通旅行 應該六四咁攤分<br />\n平時旅行攤分我ok <br />\n但度蜜月一生得一次 氹下我開心都得掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係未聽過要咁樣分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問親朋友個個都係老公俾哂<br />\n黎緊我地都會結婚 <br />\n但我感覺唔到佢有當我自己人<br />\n去旅行唔係話貴 講真兩個人加埋都係兩萬左右<br />\n我一直以為結婚後佢會對我大方d<br />\n但我應該諗多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢由始至終都鍾意錢多過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正評 當然老公比哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負評 應該兩個攤分"},{"pid":"fef1dbdb51fc3298fa9488cf7254ab9b645abe90","tid":628684,"uid":16664,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:45:58.000Z","msg":"55開"},{"pid":"19998634551b20bb3c2617b42a1cc2d47dbc845e","tid":628684,"uid":102096,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:47:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48f15022f0a862df74f7e0c981212eb72347203b","tid":628684,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:47:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a076976c62c3b8870f75eb2b9a8654cdef42b08","tid":628684,"uid":60178,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:47:26.000Z","msg":"你問得呢個問題都唔係顯得你好鐘意佢姐<br />\n有無諗過唔結咪唔洗煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b139b64985c5dc3910bf8919f7ce404b11caf443","tid":628684,"uid":21831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:48:20.000Z","msg":"每人價值觀唔同，你同佢結婚就要包埋佢個價值觀<br />\n就算今次你屈到佢請你，之後成世佢都會比說話你聽<br />\n一係你同佢傾下，佢如果咁都唔肯讓步就廢事去啦"},{"pid":"6abf41e510a48881656549ee56a7f5ee69199a6e","tid":628684,"uid":172607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a076976c62c3b8870f75eb2b9a8654cdef42b08","tid":628684,"uid":60178,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:47:26.000Z","msg":"你問得呢個問題都唔係顯得你好鐘意佢姐<br />\n有無諗過唔結咪唔洗煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:48:33.000Z","msg":"我唔鐘意佢點會同佢咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec25fbd3805b9c4554cc7ed0cd153505b5fc168f","tid":628684,"uid":69452,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:49:30.000Z","msg":"同樣地，你都係好鐘意錢"},{"pid":"318fd235d1f29e88ee28a0fb2e2d113a892966e3","tid":628684,"uid":172607,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ec25fbd3805b9c4554cc7ed0cd153505b5fc168f","tid":628684,"uid":69452,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:49:30.000Z","msg":"同樣地，你都係好鐘意錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:54:32.000Z","msg":"咁你講錯 識我嘅人都知我唔計較金錢 我請過佢去旅行"},{"pid":"9111e71fe73207143e65f91c3bfc13c631c4b3fc","tid":628684,"uid":69452,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"318fd235d1f29e88ee28a0fb2e2d113a892966e3","tid":628684,"uid":172607,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ec25fbd3805b9c4554cc7ed0cd153505b5fc168f","tid":628684,"uid":69452,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:49:30.000Z","msg":"同樣地，你都係好鐘意錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:54:32.000Z","msg":"咁你講錯 識我嘅人都知我唔計較金錢 我請過佢去旅行"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:59:06.000Z","msg":"如果係咁，你覺得邊個比真係咁重要？"},{"pid":"0d0a9ff5b054aa85b3fa11aca2012788959a3334","tid":628684,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19998634551b20bb3c2617b42a1cc2d47dbc845e","tid":628684,"uid":102096,"like":2,"dislike":3,"s